OL,3,CMurder investigation underway
OL,4,Cfollowing death of man in Plymouth
OL,6,FA 57-year-old has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder after the death of
OL,8,Fa man in Plymouth.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called just
OL,11,Fafter 8pm on Monday 4 May to reports
OL,12,Fof a serious assault of a man at a
OL,13,Fproperty on Embankment Road.
OL,15,FThe victim, a man in his 20s, had died
OL,16,Fat the scene.
OL,18,FHis next of kin have been informed and
OL,19,Fare being supported by specially
OL,20,Ftrained family liaison officers.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
