OL,3,CMurder investigation underway
OL,4,Cfollowing death of man in Plymouth
OL,6,FDetective Superintendent Rachael
OL,7,FBentley from the Major Crime
OL,8,FInvestigation Team said: "This is a
OL,9,Ftragic incident in which a man has
OL,10,Fsadly lost his life. Our thoughts are
OL,11,Fwith his family and friends at this
OL,12,Fextremely difficult time.
OL,14,F"A thorough investigation is underway
OL,15,Fto understand the full circumstances
OL,16,Fsurrounding what has happened.
OL,26,@pD@ZOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
