PN,43603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1778076676
OL,3,CMurder investigation underway
OL,4,Cfollowing death of man in Plymouth
OL,6,F"We carried out immediate searches
OL,7,Flast night which resulted in a 57-year-
OL,8,Fold man being arrested on suspicion of
OL,9,Fmurder and he is currently in police
OL,10,Fcustody.
OL,12,F"A cordon remains in place this
OL,13,Fmorning, and officers will be in the
OL,14,Farea throughout the day.
OL,16,F"Police are appealing for anyone who
OL,17,Fwitnessed the incident, or who was in
OL,18,Fthe area at the time, to come forward."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
