OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1778076676
OL,3,CMurder investigation underway
OL,4,Cfollowing death of man in Plymouth
OL,6,FDet Supt Bentley added: "At this
OL,7,Fstage, this is believed to be an
OL,8,Fisolated incident with no wider risk
OL,9,Fto the public. We are not seeking
OL,10,Fanyone else in connection with the
OL,11,Fincident.
OL,13,F"We are particularly keen to hear from
OL,14,Fanyone who was in and around the area
OL,15,Fof Embankment Road yesterday evening
OL,16,Fand may have seen or heard anything
OL,17,Fsuspicious. Even information that may
OL,18,Fseem small could be vital to our
OL,19,Finvestigation."
OL,26,@nD@YOUuD@AOU{D@OO]
